<SLUG> BC-R-INDEPENDENT-COUNSELS-REVIEW-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
IN HOT PURSUIT OF MINUTIAE: THE SOUND OF ONE LAW BREAKING DOWN
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(ART ADV: Graphic list of independent counsels is being sent to NYT
graphic clients. Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by
calling (888) 603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(bl) 
By DAVID JOHNSTON   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
