<HEADLINE>
A MOTHER COUNTRY'S ADVICE: DO AS I SAY, NOT AS I DID 
</HEADLINE>
 
 (Repeating for all needing.)   (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
 By ALAN RIDING   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   In the early 1980s, as many South American countries were
preparing to switch from military to civilian rule, they were
