in Japan 1615-1868'' is on exhibit at the National Gallery of Art
until Feb. 15. But two programs, Exploring Edo and Virtual Edo, are
available for free on CD-ROM and the Internet. (Clothier, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) MOVED
</P>
