<P>
   A Boston Globe article about Nexar Technologies Inc. contained
incorrect company information and outdated SEC information. Palomar
Technologies Inc., which provided $22.8 million in capital to
launch Nexar in 1995, said it was repaid $6.7 million after Nexar's
April 1997 initial public stock offering. Also, Palomar spokesman
John Ingoldsby said none of Nexar's directors have been affiliated
with Palomar since December 1997.
</P>
