longer recovery time. By Larry Tye. 800 words. (s and a coding)
</P>
<P>
   FBN-RYAN-COLUMN (Undated) _ The Ship of Fools that is the
Connecticut legislature will set sail sometime Tuesday.
Destination: Poor House. By Bob Ryan.
</P>
