<SLUG> BC-COURT-WHISTLEBLOWER-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
COURT RULES THAT WHISTLE-BLOWER CAN SUE COMPANY 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: FILED in ``f'' and ``w'' categories)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By MARK HELM  
 c.1998 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ In a decision that could help whistle-blowers, the
