<P>
   MATTEL-LEARNING (Undated) _ Mattel Inc., the world's largest toy
maker, said Monday that it had agreed to acquire the Learning Co.
in a $3.8-billion stock deal that would position the company as a
leader in the fast-growing market for educational and entertainment
software.
</P>
<P>
   (We plan to move this story by 9 p.m. ET in `f' news file.)
</P>
